            "author": 2356,
            "body": "<p>我们一定要反对党内一小撮反动分子的分裂阴谋，维护长者的和香港记者们谈笑风生的权威！</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20181103/1541243673195589.jpg\" title=\"1541243673195589.jpg\" alt=\"images (17).jpg\"></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20181103/1541243696307127.jpeg\" title=\"1541243696307127.jpeg\" alt=\"db8e534e499c458ebd21ea44026aca78.jpeg\"></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20181103/1541243726281417.jpg\" title=\"1541243726281417.jpg\" alt=\"世界国际革命.jpg\"></p>",
